latestPosts.caption:
“Beyond the stars where silence sings, I know you wait with open wings. One day, I’ll find you in the light, And we’ll set off, no end in sight. All the roads we left undone— We’ll walk them slow beneath the sun. Until that day, just wait for me, Where dreams run wild and souls run free.”

Marks a whole year today without you, but not a single day has passed me by that I haven’t thought how it would’ve been if you were here. After every bad session I still wish to ping you and hear the most amazing motivational speech ever(and how can I ever forget the moving on one, hilarious to the core). But we know you’ll be always there to catch me when I fall. I miss you with every climb.
I LOVE YOU WITH ALL MY HEART, always and forever^^
